			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>Flames encircle the end of this black and gold wand.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Implement</b><b>:</b> Rod</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Critical:</b> +4d6 fire critical damage</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Property:</b></p> <p>When you hit an enemy with a fire or radiant attack power using this rod and deal damage to it, that enemy grants combat advantage to you on your next attack against it before the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power (Minor Action)</b></p><p>Green flame bursts from the end of the rod, illuminating the area around you like a torch. You can end this effect as a free action.</p>",
